<BaseLayout
  title="数据来源"
  description="澳洲百科的全部公开数据源清单——澳大利亚统计局、外交贸易部、内政部、储备银行、学术数据库等。"
>
  <article class="max-w-editorial mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-aus-ink font-bold mb-8">数据来源</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p>澳洲百科的所有条目基于以下公开政府数据与学术资源。每篇文章末尾附有具体的条目级引用来源。</p>

      <h2 class="font-heading text-xl">政府机构</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Australian Bureau of Statistics (ABS)</strong> — abs.gov.au · 人口普查、经济指标、社会统计</li>
        <li><strong>Department of Foreign Affairs and Trade (DFAT)</strong> — dfat.gov.au · 外交政策、贸易协定、FTA 网络</li>
        <li><strong>Department of Home Affairs</strong> — homeaffairs.gov.au · 移民政策、签证类别、公民入籍</li>
        <li><strong>Reserve Bank of Australia (RBA)</strong> — rba.gov.au · 货币政策、利率、金融稳定</li>
        <li><strong>Geoscience Australia</strong> — ga.gov.au · 地理、地质、矿产资源</li>
        <li><strong>Bureau of Meteorology (BOM)</strong> — bom.gov.au · 气候、气象数据</li>
        <li><strong>Australian Institute of Health and Welfare (AIHW)</strong> — aihw.gov.au · 健康、福利统计</li>
        <li><strong>Austrade</strong> — austrade.gov.au · 贸易与投资数据</li>
        <li><strong>Australian Electoral Commission (AEC)</strong> — aec.gov.au · 选举制度与数据</li>
        <li><strong>Parliament of Australia</strong> — aph.gov.au · 立法、议会记录</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-heading text-xl">学术资源</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Australian Historical Studies</strong> (journal) — 澳洲历史研究</li>
        <li><strong>Australian Journal of Political Science</strong> — 澳洲政治科学</li>
        <li><strong>Australian Economic Review</strong> — 澳洲经济研究</li>
        <li><strong>National Library of Australia (Trove)</strong> — trove.nla.gov.au · 澳洲历史文献与报纸数字化档案</li>
        <li><strong>Australian Institute of Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander Studies (AIATSIS)</strong> — aiatsis.gov.au · 原住民研究</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
